If no one  has given you one of those "I did this and it worked great" ideas
I would stick with a new used bell housing to keep things simple.
I would check the pilot bearing in the flywheel to make sure your input
shaft isn't the reason the seal and sleeve failed in the first place.(due to
chattering)
Good luck
Brian
